title: Cigköftem
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Was veg but added meat per 2015 report. Turkish fast food franchise offering a vegan vegetable pate made of grains, walnut, tomato puree, sunflower oil, parsley, and green onion, which are formed into little balls or fingers and place inside wraps or on mixed plates. Main product is vegan kéfte. Yogurt drink is dairy based.
